                        <h1 class="start-screen__title">Not only people<br>
                            need a house</h1>
                        <p class="start-screen__text">We offer to give a chance to a little and nice puppy with an
                            extremely wide and open heart. He or she will love you more than anybody else in the world,
                            you will see!</p>
                        <div class="start-screen__btn"><a class="button" href="#friends">Make a friend</a></div>
                    </div>
